[Annotator "https://lichess.org/@/RushConnectedPawns"]
[FEN "2rr2k1/ppq1bppp/2p5/8/3P4/1P6/PBQ2PPP/R4RK1 b - - 0 1"]
[SetUp "1"]
[UTCDate "2026.06.03"]
[UTCTime "23:54:55"]
[ChapterMode "gamebook"]

{ Let's ask the 3 'Golden Strategy' questions!
1. What is my worst placed piece? (R on c8)
2. What are the weaknesses? (d4)
3. What is my opponent's plan? (None)

Find black's best move! }
1... Bf6! 2. Rad1 Rd5! { Blockading the isolated pawn (review the 'Isolated Pawn' chapter)! } (2... Rd6?! { Why not blockade the pawn? }) (2... Rd7?! { Why not blockade the pawn? }) (2... Qf4?! { Why not blockade the pawn? }) (2... Qb6?! { Why not blockade the pawn? }) 3. Rd2 Rcd8! (3... Qd7!? { Also works. Play Rcd8 for the solution. }) 4. Rfd1 Qd7 $17 { White's pieces are tied up to the weakness and black is much better. } (4... Qd6!? { Also works. Play Qd7 for the solution. }) *


