[UTCTime "23:54:55"]
[ChapterMode "gamebook"]

{ This position has arisen from a famous opening. Let's evaluate and ask the 3 positional questions:
1. What is my worst placed piece? (Bishop on f1)
2. What are the weaknesses? (None)
3. What is my opponent's plan? (Probably Bb4 after Nc3...)

Find white's most logical move! }
4. a3! { We stop black's main idea of going Bb4 and prepare Nc3 next! } { [%csl Gb4][%cal Bf8b4,Ga3b4] } (4. Nc3?! { This is also a move, but it allows Bb4 pinning your knight... } 4... Bb4) *


